Madeira’s Debt May Be About 5 Billion Euros, Jardim Tells RTP

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-09-23T07:13:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/madeira-s-debt-may-be-about-5-billion-euros-jardim-tells-rtp.html
The debt of the Portuguese island
region of Madeira may be about 5 billion euros ($6.8 billion),
broadcaster RTP said, citing Alberto Joao Jardim, the leader of
the region’s ruling PSD-Madeira party.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
